{"tid":744721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新華社：中國可能最快明年舉辦世冠盃","createTime":"2018-07-16T07:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T08:55:34.000Z","uid":31907,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"10e4da61a21a4ec3a06dfbce899df8acd4215714","tid":744721,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:06:16.000Z","msg":"《新華社》報導，阿里巴巴董事局主席馬雲與國際足協(FIFA)會長恩芬天奴會面，有份參與會面的阿里體育CEO張大鐘透露，有關會面是工作會談，長達一個多小時，「雙方聊得很嗨」，馬雲代表中國企業家，為國際足球提出很多新的想法。雙方的討論提及，世界冠軍球會盃最快明年可能落戶中國。<br />\n<br />\n報導引述張大鐘表示，雙方在世冠盃等問題上深入交流，並就中國舉辦世冠盃指出「2019年和2020年很有可能，很有希望，但還是有很多程序要走」。他又說，國際足協也希望世冠盃在中國舉辦，將積極推進。而之前國際足協推動世冠盃改革擴軍，馬雲亦非常支持。<br />\n<br />\n全武鬥！！！冇球星敢入國家隊......"},{"pid":"c38169b337c244b1f02814b51b32e1f62e4cb60e","tid":744721,"uid":93831,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:09:30.000Z","msg":"國乜撚野家隊呀你老母"},{"pid":"7e10eeea2f74203679bb4f3ad85dfa5f379594bf","tid":744721,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:16:39.000Z","msg":"食屎啦"},{"pid":"80b9cb0d22cb5820738350d6b14547198a88ca5a","tid":744721,"uid":1096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:17:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/151703_44eaef176c2e37908930032babd41fc9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F151703_44eaef176c2e37908930032babd41fc9.png&h=ca4e533e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c67db06d51cd55aaa7b5bbbf2625ea2818bb1a2","tid":744721,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:18:50.000Z","msg":"支那可以表演即場賄賂球証<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a26b7eebc499247acf307844aa44496a1bdc3e","tid":744721,"uid":13205,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:27:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.qiushibaike.com/article/33943269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiushibaike.com%2Farticle%2F33943269&d=Hsg6bBXkDCZF%2F1K4r0b0JcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ef398820\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiushibaike.com/article/33943269</a><br />\n（殘體慎入）<br />\n<blockquote>中國想再次進入世界盃只有一個辦法：<br />\n1、通過運作，讓國際足聯分配一個名額給南極洲；<br />\n2、讓中國隊加入南極洲賽區；<br />\n3、由中國隊與企鵝爭奪出線權；<br />\n4、中國隊客場逼平企鵝；<br />\n5、主場安排在三亞，熱死企鵝後出線。<br />\n<br />\n但目前看來，第4步還挺困難&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbea74ca16eb27942143870f47be7f0e61059c41","tid":744721,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"66a26b7eebc499247acf307844aa44496a1bdc3e","tid":744721,"uid":13205,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:27:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.qiushibaike.com/article/33943269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiushibaike.com%2Farticle%2F33943269&d=Hsg6bBXkDCZF%2F1K4r0b0JcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ef398820\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiushibaike.com/article/33943269</a><br />\n（殘體慎入）<br />\n<blockquote>中國想再次進入世界盃只有一個辦法：<br />\n1、通過運作，讓國際足聯分配一個名額給南極洲；<br />\n2、讓中國隊加入南極洲賽區；<br />\n3、由中國隊與企鵝爭奪出線權；<br />\n4、中國隊客場逼平企鵝；<br />\n5、主場安排在三亞，熱死企鵝後出線。<br />\n<br />\n但目前看來，第4步還挺困難&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:40:39.000Z","msg":"笑死,<br />\n其實依家中國出線決賽周都係五五波姐,可以取代南韓或者沙特,雖然只係取代佢哋做魚腩"},{"pid":"d7b1485177dd870e1dbdd6703b373d7fd8942238","tid":744721,"uid":191762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"其實世冠...個人覺得啟德開咗之後香港有得諗<br />\n好過搞亞運<br />\n<br />\n中國話知佢啦"},{"pid":"daf2c70ff809521fcdcb9603e82f9295595b4261","tid":744721,"uid":86898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7b1485177dd870e1dbdd6703b373d7fd8942238","tid":744721,"uid":191762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"其實世冠...個人覺得啟德開咗之後香港有得諗<br />\n好過搞亞運<br />\n<br /